{"tid":564413,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"點解萬綺雯47歲仲可以咁好J？","createTime":"2018-02-18T03:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T06:32:32.000Z","uid":40525,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c5d636f7d16fbcbe966bacd2042e7370d942cf","tid":564413,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T03:19:56.000Z","msg":"現年四十七的萬綺雯（蚊蚊）向來有凍齡長腿女神稱號，早前與好友歐陽震華（Bobby）在上海演出舞台劇《紙飛機的天空》，最後一幕以孖辮校服造型現身，大家都驚歎她是逆齡生長，蚊蚊感謝網民對她外表的讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/111924_df73b70642eb078c8ae223a6e6c05130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F111924_df73b70642eb078c8ae223a6e6c05130.jpg&h=5f2a3a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蚊蚊與 Bobby 曾在劇集《東坡家事》合作，二人早前再拍檔演舞台劇《紙飛機的天空》自然默契十足，「一直演出都很有火花，劇中加了很多我對他的家暴劇情，打完又錫，錫完又氹，十八般武藝出齊，大家見我不停打他，都很驚我。不過其實很開心，國內觀眾反應很好，Bobby 在台上揮灑自如，觀眾在中途也鼓掌，Bobby 提議再有舞台劇也要繼續一起合作，電視劇也再要一起拍檔，我當然開心，我們互相承諾下一套劇要合作，如果有機會選對手，一定不用考慮就選對方。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2EOmlgh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2EOmlgh&d=ePnc8nuz0lVNRm5%2BXZzth54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=33dcdd2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2EOmlgh</a>"},{"pid":"1c1ac8fefaab3acb03bba6eb4d3a08be3ee17f73","tid":564413,"uid":49151,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"好樣衰"},{"pid":"bf504f22c8293991167e842c3c25dbed5a0ef927","tid":564413,"uid":130901,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T03:27:48.000Z","msg":"其實一向都唔好j"},{"pid":"c8c6af0a15437bee3bbf5c6948adf3e48c50e6f8","tid":564413,"uid":167658,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"諗起把煙鏟沙喉聲發姣就想嘔"},{"pid":"4100fa61f714be919c956f92aaee5c2531f3e929","tid":564413,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{